{"tid":1876421,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"政府撥逾228萬予兩機構賑濟菲律賓風災災民","createTime":"2020-02-12T11:26:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T11:54:54.000Z","uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"21c3d142017b88230d2eab8b9540e3904b5e9a7d","tid":1876421,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:26:38.000Z","msg":"特區政府撥款228萬多元予兩間機構，賑濟菲律賓風災的災民。 政府發言人表示，接納賑災基金諮詢委員建議，分別批出逾76萬及152萬元予安澤中國（香港）救援協會及樂施會。撥款會用於提供家庭和衛生用品，以及臨時居所物料，約2萬4500名災民受惠，兩間救援機構將會進行賑災的地點並不相同，並沒有資源重疊。"},{"pid":"5e9c9a0619a0c385fa69edf34a429ab7b50a979b","tid":1876421,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:27:27.000Z","msg":"有冇捐埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f1a1948ad56d1d7b3ed6e315e9ffa7fc6ab81c","tid":1876421,"uid":22609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:42:22.000Z","msg":"菲律賓最近都無打過風<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aba35a3763ab97f71e98fa3096e2de501fd0cee","tid":1876421,"uid":83713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:47:17.000Z","msg":"菲律賓最近有打風咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"469be617b32a01e5f6efc2115b78ac3968f79fd1","tid":1876421,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2aba35a3763ab97f71e98fa3096e2de501fd0cee","tid":1876421,"uid":83713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:47:17.000Z","msg":"菲律賓最近有打風咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji